description:
Enjoy the video of Mariatta Wijaya in which she invites the entire community to participate in Pycon Colombia 2022.

Social Networks:

Github: https://github.com/Mariatta
Twitter: https://twitter.com/mariatta
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/mariatta/

Pycon Colombia 2022 in this edition brings great guests and this year we will have the participation of Mariatta Wijaya, She is a Python core developer and contributes to various open-source projects. She currently works as Senior Developer Relations Engineer at Google. 

This is the beginning of great announcements, follow us on our social networks so you don't miss any updates.

Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/pyconcolombia
